Sequence Information.Peptide Name: Tn-AFP1 (Trapa natans antifungal peptide; Plant defensin)
Sequence Information.Hemolytic Activity: Tn-AFP1 has no adverse effect on red blood cells at concentration of 32 μg mL−1
Sequence Information.Cytotoxicity: No cytotoxicity information found in the reference(s) presented
Sequence Information.Function: Tn-AFP1 has no adverse effect on red blood cells at concentration of 32 μg/mL.

Literature.Title: Identification of an antifungal peptide from Trapa natans fruits with inhibitory effects on Candida tropicalis biofilm formation.
Literature.Author: Mandal SM, Migliolo L, Franco OL, Ghosh AK.
